# Override the parent gitignore for this examples directory: we WANT to
# track the .mumei/ tree here so the artifacts are visible to readers
# browsing examples/ without installing mumei.
!.mumei/
!.mumei/**

# Keep `current` (per-developer cursor) ignored even in the example —
# matches mumei's actual layout (a fresh clone has no active cursor).
# `state.json` is INTENTIONALLY tracked here even though mumei's normal
# `.mumei/.gitignore` excludes it — the example's purpose (REQ-5.19) is to
# expose every artifact a reader would see, including the state snapshot.
.mumei/current
